worth 100 times the entire global economy, enough for every person on

00:19:10.238 --> 00:19:17.338
Earth to receive around $1.25 billion, so what would be the impact of that?

00:19:18.278 --> 00:19:22.585
Well, everyone on Earth wouldn’t receive $1.25 billion.

00:19:23.318 --> 00:19:28.338
This 10 quintillion dollar number is the estimated total value of

00:19:28.495 --> 00:19:32.778
all the precious metals in that asteroid at current market prices.

