Because of the timelines of getting there, the cost of a mission, and the fact that a spacecraft is

00:19:54.848 --> 00:20:01.338
limited to how much it can carry back, it would take hundreds if not thousands of years for even a

00:20:01.358 --> 00:20:07.398
fraction of the precious metals on an asteroid this size to be mined and then brought back to Earth.

