Still, there are some commentators who have pointed out that, even with a relatively

00:20:13.435 --> 00:20:18.785
small haul of precious metals, asteroid mining could be very detrimental to

00:20:18.825 --> 00:20:23.305
lower-income countries that have so-far relied on natural resource extraction.

00:20:23.975 --> 00:20:28.755
Mines back on Earth would be closed, millions of people would be out of a job,

00:20:29.245 --> 00:20:33.405
and there would need to be some sort of mechanism for these countries to be

00:20:33.445 --> 00:20:38.535
compensated by the countries or companies that enjoyed the spoils of asteroid mining.

00:20:39.845 --> 00:20:44.205
There are also environmental concerns, but these are mainly the concerns

00:20:44.215 --> 00:20:49.315
about space pollution, of debris from the mines floating around in space.

00:20:50.695 --> 00:20:55.776
In terms of environmental concerns on Earth, it seems pretty clear-cut.

